    <title type="html"><![CDATA[02_CUDR]]></title>
    <link href="http://JonneyYan.github.io/blog/2014/07/31/02-cudr/"/>
    <updated>2014-07-31T22:43:45+08:00</updated>
    <id>http://JonneyYan.github.io/blog/2014/07/31/02-cudr</id>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1>插入（Insert）</h1>

<h2>insert()</h2>

<ul>
<li>该方法会自动给文档增加一个_id键</li>
</ul>


<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>&gt;db.foo.insert({"bar" : "barz"})</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<h2>batchInsert()</h2>

<ul>
<li>只能一次插入到单个集合中</li>
<li>中间有错误，后面的停止插入</li>
<li>可以使用<code>continueOnError</code>选项忽略错误,shell不支持，驱动程序支持</li>
</ul>


<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>&gt;db.foo.batchInsert( [{"_id" : 0}, {"_id" : 1}, {"_id" : 2}])</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<h1>删除（Delete）</h1>

<h2>删除所有文档, 但不删除集合</h2>

<blockquote><p>db.foo.remove()</p></blockquote>

<h2>删除单个文档</h2>

<blockquote><p>db.foo.remove({&ldquo;opt-put&rdquo; : true})</p></blockquote>

<h2>删除集合</h2>

<blockquote><p>db.foo.drop()</p></blockquote>

<h1>更新(Update)</h1>

<h2>文档替换</h2>

<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>&gt;db.foo.update({"name" : "jonney"}, jony)</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<blockquote><p><em>Note</em>:当使用<code>update</code>更新文档时，可能会遇到update的查询条件匹配到了多个文档，这时需要使用_id作为查询条件：
db.people.update({&ldquo;id&rdquo; : ObjectId(&ldquo;1233242134sd14sf1234134ssd&rdquo;)}, jony})</p></blockquote>

<h2>修改器（Modifier）</h2>

<h3>$set</h3>

<ul>
<li>用来指定一个字段的值，如果这个字段不存在，则创建他。</li>
<li>可以修改字段的类型，例如将一个字段改为数组</li>
<li>使用<code>$unset</code>删除键</li>
<li>可以修改内嵌文档</li>
</ul>


<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
<span class='line-number'>4</span>
<span class='line-number'>5</span>
<span class='line-number'>6</span>
<span class='line-number'>7</span>
<span class='line-number'>8</span>
<span class='line-number'>9</span>
<span class='line-number'>10</span>
<span class='line-number'>11</span>
<span class='line-number'>12</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>&gt;db.foo.update(
</span><span class='line'>        {"name" : "jony"}, 
</span><span class='line'>        {"$set" : {"sex" : "famel"}}
</span><span class='line'>    )
</span><span class='line'>&gt;db.foo.update(
</span><span class='line'>        {"name" : "Jonney"},
</span><span class='line'>        {"$unset" : { "name" : 1}}
</span><span class='line'>    )
</span><span class='line'>&gt;db.foo.update(
</span><span class='line'>        {"name" : "Jonney"},
</span><span class='line'>        {"$set" : {"address.street" : "abc"}}
</span><span class='line'>    )</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<h3>$inc</h3>

<ul>
<li>用来增加或减少键的值，如果字段不存在，则创建它</li>
<li>只能用于数值类型的值</li>
</ul>


<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
<span class='line-number'>4</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>&gt;db.foo.update(
</span><span class='line'>        {"name" : "jonney"},
</span><span class='line'>        {"$inc" : {"age" : 10}}
</span><span class='line'>    )</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<h3>数组修改器</h3>

<ul>
<li><code>$push</code> 向数组末尾添加一个元素

<ul>
<li>$each 添加多个元素</li>
<li>$slice 保证数组不会超过设定好的最大长度</li>
<li>$sort 超过$slice指定的长度时，将元素排序，并保留前xx个元素</li>
<li>$sort 和 $slice需要配合$each使用</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>


<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
<span class='line-number'>4</span>
<span class='line-number'>5</span>
<span class='line-number'>6</span>
<span class='line-number'>7</span>
<span class='line-number'>8</span>
<span class='line-number'>9</span>
<span class='line-number'>10</span>
<span class='line-number'>11</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>&gt;db.foo.update(
</span><span class='line'>        {"name" : "Jonney"},
</span><span class='line'>        {"$push", {"friend" : {
</span><span class='line'>            "$each" : [{"name" : "Tim", "age" : 12},
</span><span class='line'>                       {"name" : "Jony", "age" : 21}
</span><span class='line'>                      ],
</span><span class='line'>            "$slice" : -10,
</span><span class='line'>            "$sort" : {"age" : -1}
</span><span class='line'>            }   
</span><span class='line'>        }}
</span><span class='line'>    )</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<ul>
<li><code>$ne</code> &amp;&amp; <code>$addToSet</code> 将数组当做数据集（set）操作

<ul>
<li><code>$addToSet</code> 可以和<code>$each</code>配合使用</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>


<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
<span class='line-number'>4</span>
<span class='line-number'>5</span>
<span class='line-number'>6</span>
<span class='line-number'>7</span>
<span class='line-number'>8</span>
<span class='line-number'>9</span>
<span class='line-number'>10</span>
<span class='line-number'>11</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>&gt;db.foo.update({"emails" : {"$ne" : "jony@gamil.com"}},
</span><span class='line'>    {"$push" : {"emails" : "jony@gamil.com"}}
</span><span class='line'>)
</span><span class='line'>&gt;db.foo.update({"_id" : ObjectId(12df31fdf2df233f12a)},
</span><span class='line'>    {"$addToSet" : 
</span><span class='line'>        {"emails" : 
</span><span class='line'>            {"$each" : ["jonney@gmail.com", "tom@gmail.com", "cook@gmail.com"]
</span><span class='line'>            }
</span><span class='line'>        }
</span><span class='line'>    }
</span><span class='line'>)</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<ul>
<li><code>$pop</code> &amp;&amp; <code>$pull</code>  删除元素

<ul>
<li><code>$pop</code> 将数组看成队列或者栈</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>


<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>&gt;db.list.update({}, {"$pop" : {"todo" : "1"}})  //从数组末尾删除
</span><span class='line'>&gt;db.list.update({}, {"$pop" : {"todo" : "-1"}}) //从数组头部删除</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<pre><code>- `$pull` 会将数组中所有匹配的文档删除, 例如`[1,2,3,1,1]`,执行`pull 1`结果为`[2,3]`
</code></pre>

<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>&gt;db.list.update({}, {"$pull" : {"todo" : "dishes"}})</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<ul>
<li>基于位置的数组修改器

<ul>
<li>使用数组的下标</li>
<li>使用$定位操作符</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>


<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
<span class='line-number'>4</span>
<span class='line-number'>5</span>
<span class='line-number'>6</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>&gt;db.bolg.update({"post" : post_id}, 
</span><span class='line'>        {"$inc" : {"comment.0.votes" : 1}}
</span><span class='line'>    })
</span><span class='line'>&gt;db.blog.update({"comment.author" : "jonney"},
</span><span class='line'>    {"$set", {"comment.$.author" : "Cook"}}
</span><span class='line'>)</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<h3>修改器的速度</h3>

<ul>
<li>Mongodb 文档的存储方式：

<ul>
<li>当文档被插入时，MongoDB会将文档依次存入硬盘
  |&ldquo;x&rdquo; : &ldquo;a&rdquo;| |&ldquo;x&rdquo; : &ldquo;b&rdquo;| |&ldquo;x&rdquo; : &ldquo;c&rdquo;|</li>
<li>在对中间的文档进行修改，使其尺寸变大，该文档就会被移动到集合的尾部.此时会修改集合的填充因子（<code>padding factor</code>）使其从1变为1.5
  |&ldquo;x&rdquo; : &ldquo;a&rdquo;|             |&ldquo;x&rdquo; : &ldquo;c&rdquo;| |&ldquo;x&rdquo; : &ldquo;bbb&rdquo;|</li>
<li>所以，对于$inc和不发生文档变化的$set修改器，执行的速度是很快的</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>


<h2>合并 || 迁移（upsert）</h2>

<ul>
<li>upsert 是一种特殊的更新，如果查找到符合的文档，就会正常更新，如果没有查找到符合的文档，那么就会以查询的文档和更新文档共同创建一个新的文档。这就相当于将查询条件看成是Master， 将更新文档合并到Master上。</li>
</ul>


<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>&gt;db.analytics.update({"url" : "/blog"}, {"$inc" : {"pageview" : 1}}， true)</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<pre><code>- 原子操作
</code></pre>

<ul>
<li><code>$setOnInsert</code> 只在创建字段时赋值，之后字段的值不再改变</li>
</ul>


<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>&gt;db.users.update({"$setOnInsert" : {"createAt" : new Date()}}, true)</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<ul>
<li>save (shell程序)

<ul>
<li>如果文档不存在，创建文档并插入；</li>
<li>如果文档存在，更新文档</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>


<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>&gt;db.foo.save(x)</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<h2>更新多个文档</h2>

<ul>
<li>默认情况下更新只对匹配到的第一个文件进行更新，如果想要更新多个文档，需要将update的第4个参数设置为true。</li>
</ul>


<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>&gt;db.users.update({"birthday" : "10/13/2014"}, 
</span><span class='line'>    {"$set" : {"gift" : "Happy Birthday"}}, false, true
</span><span class='line'>)</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<ul>
<li><code>findAndModify</code> 命令可以查找元素并返回更新后的文档</li>
</ul>


<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
<span class='line-number'>4</span>
<span class='line-number'>5</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>&gt;db.runCommend({"findAndModify" : "processes",
</span><span class='line'>    "query" : {"state" : "READY"},
</span><span class='line'>    "sort" : {"priority" : -1},
</span><span class='line'>    "update" : {"$set" : "RUNNINGS"}
</span><span class='line'>})</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<ul>
<li><code>findAndModify</code> 命令可以使用的字段：

<ul>
<li>query</li>
<li>sort</li>
<li>update</li>
<li>remove</li>
<li>new</li>
<li>fields</li>
<li>upsert</li>
<li><code>update</code> 和 <code>remove</code> 必须有一个，且只能有一个。</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>


<h1>写入安全（Write Concern）</h1>

<ul>
<li>应答式写入(acknowledged write) 数据库给出响应</li>
<li>非应答式写入(unacknowledged write)</li>
</ul>

]]></content>
